&lt;p&gt;I won&apos;t grant a license for it, though, since I didn&apos;t do the original work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hopefully this saves the submitter a little work.  If they can just sign off on this file, they shouldn&apos;t need to deal with any other details.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
