(more)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, I just realized - the configure.ac file should be updated for the new functions used (notice gethostbyname is there in .ac file, need to add strtok_r, getaddrinfo, etc... ).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Might also be a good idea to verify this build on window/linux/freebsd. It built fine on ubuntu.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
